longBusinessSummary: Cohance Lifesciences Limited engage in the end-to-end contract development and manufacturing of intermediates and active pharmaceutical ingredients in India. The coampny offers active pharmaceutical ingredients and formulations for various applications; CDMO services, a flexible and custom solutions for challenging development and manufacturing needs; and clinical, analytical, and research services. It also manufactures finished dosage formulations for pharmaceutical companies; and specialty chemicals, such as electronic chemicals. The company was formerly known as Suven Pharmaceuticals Limited and changed its name to Cohance Lifesciences Limited in May 2025. The company was founded in 1989 and is based in Hyderabad, India. Cohance Lifesciences Limited is a subsidiary of Berhyanda Limited.
